summary:
Sourcing & Recruitment - Talent Acquisition Specialist @ Bunge 

Bunge is a global leader in sourcing, processing and supplying oilseed and grain products and ingredients. Bungeâ€™s expansive network feeds and fuels a growing world, creating sustainable products and opportunities for more than 70,000 farmers and the consumers they serve across the globe. 
Founded in 1818 (in Amsterdam ðŸ˜Š) and now headquartered in St. Louis, Missouri, with over 25,000 employees, we stand behind more than 350 port terminals, oilseed processing plants, grain facilities, and food production & packaging facilities around the world.

Do you want to make a difference as part of a growing and innovative leader in the food industry? Join our global network of local and international experts and be part of an exciting and essential business where an entrepreneurial mindset is valued! 

Check bunge.com/careers for more information. Set a job alert or apply immediately via jobs.bunge.com.
